    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >古代的魔法阵已经减弱，怪物出现了。与圣者一起修复魔法阵，阻止黑暗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/6677497c809b3b7467d41346c471bf5e.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=800 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/6677497c809b3b7467d41346c471bf5e.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/6677497c809b3b7467d41346c471bf5e.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《救救我吧，我的英雄》</strong>是一款具有类Roguelike元素的防御游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过英雄的多种技能和特殊能力，打造属于你自己的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创造属于你自己的英雄。</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种道具和技能强化英雄的能力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/35f47e8c4fb79069436eba013b25f4b6.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/35f47e8c4fb79069436eba013b25f4b6.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/35f47e8c4fb79069436eba013b25f4b6.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/0919c6788145ba588e67eacb5e5c7654.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/0919c6788145ba588e67eacb5e5c7654.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/0919c6788145ba588e67eacb5e5c7654.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d06a7fc3947247a2138ac883eb557336.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d06a7fc3947247a2138ac883eb557336.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d06a7fc3947247a2138ac883eb557336.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使是相同的英雄，根据装备的道具和技能，战斗方式也会不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过各种技能和道具打造英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/60d5b3cb12554777575100975e03dc8e.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/60d5b3cb12554777575100975e03dc8e.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/60d5b3cb12554777575100975e03dc8e.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/1828660be798aa1b7d11481f4d84ea86.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/1828660be798aa1b7d11481f4d84ea86.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/1828660be798aa1b7d11481f4d84ea86.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/4a937aab6a9bb8b6c0962ecb4520ff7b.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/4a937aab6a9bb8b6c0962ecb4520ff7b.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/4a937aab6a9bb8b6c0962ecb4520ff7b.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>保护圣者并合作。</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣者在各种情况下帮助英雄。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣者恢复英雄的生命并攻击怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d98ac0b76833e31ca58190095f879dbf.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d98ac0b76833e31ca58190095f879dbf.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d98ac0b76833e31ca58190095f879dbf.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/4542b42619a739be6fb178175fd4ec9f.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/4542b42619a739be6fb178175fd4ec9f.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/4542b42619a739be6fb178175fd4ec9f.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/1a8e6b2e2a5281dc6c1845ac20f20e79.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/1a8e6b2e2a5281dc6c1845ac20f20e79.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/1a8e6b2e2a5281dc6c1845ac20f20e79.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
